{"tid":1500990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個人建議，二段遊行去彩虹坐港鐵","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T08:26:40.000Z","uid":195193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aba7057c553edb3ff2120b4cb66fc14960a45ee8","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"人在現場，身邊人都認同，推俾大家<br />\n<br />\n同佢係偉業街企定定打對台，時間一拖長我地失利，俾時間佢地增援部署，和理非未入夜開始散，天一黑又TG 放題<br />\n<br />\n佢玩到封港鐵咁大<br />\n就打蛇隨棍上，放棄陣地戰<br />\n全部人set個時間，例如5:00二段遊行，沿偉業街北上入觀塘道到彩虹港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n人夠多效果明顯，示威目的達成，又减少損兵折將，為聽日留力<br />\n<br />\n非膠，只係建議"},{"pid":"5454133775f017d5e372bd57f67eaade265b2867","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cf9831f879d86a95436d663e46a4927baf8de5e1","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4f6ef969c7b86cfa0863c7b017d27f11784222ca","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"560d63adf1203a346985e4deb4971d488f260f71","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"67e74f60f52c2fc00d9e4f5be8c2d7043c5ebed5","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9e299f050fb22ec76694155a96e2ab0f3b200e09","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bbb2dbf9b97dddfe1a1bdb979944f3137836faf0","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"714e9c9f9d61f6c415a437b43c0ea75fd4286ebc","tid":1500990,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f819204f7ddfa